HEADWORD: Xantho-
<hw>Xan"tho-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A combining form from Gr.
<grk>xanqo`s</grk> yellow; as in <ex>xantho</ex>cobaltic salts. Used
also adjectively in chemistry.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Xanthocarpous</ent>⟦br⟧
